Name: greenwood
Description: Greenwood is your full-stack workbench for the web, focused on supporting modern web standards and development to help you create your next project.

Packages.Name: greenwood
Packages.Description: Your workbench for the web.  Focused on supporting modern web standards and development to help you create your next project.

Packages.Name: @greenwood/init
Packages.Description: A package for scaffolding a new Greenwood project.

Packages.Description: A Greenwood plugin for supporting Netlify serverless and edge runtimes.

Packages.Name: @greenwood/plugin-adapter-vercel
Packages.Description: A Greenwood plugin for supporting Vercel serverless and edge runtimes.

Packages.Description: A Greenwood plugin for using Babel and applying it to your JavaScript.
